      <hedline>
        <hl1>Fuzzy Little Test Tubes</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Janet Robinson Kottler letter praises Lawrence Osborne's personal insights and humor in July 30 article on lab micee</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Rarely have I so enjoyed an article on so gruesome a topic. Lawrence Osborne (July 30) provided facts along with personal insights and humor while presenting a moral dilemma. Catherine Chalmers's photographs made an eloquent statement, too. The article went right to my heart, though I have no answers.</p>
        <p>Janet Robinson Kottler  Boca Raton, Fla.</p>
      </block>
